---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(59,130,246,.55),transparent_60%)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -right-20 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(236,72,153,.45),transparent_60%)]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="service-hero">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-cyan-400"></span>
        <span class="uppercase tracking-[0.20em] text-[11px] font-medium text-neutral-600/80">Treatment</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">Hydrafacial® / Deep Cleanse</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl muted measure leading-relaxed">Cleansing, extraction, and intensive hydration for an instant, camera‑ready glow.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-80">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border rule/70 bg-white/40 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 md:p-5">
        <div class="h-24 w-full rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-300/40 via-cyan-300/35 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-neutral-300/70 dark:via-white/15 to-transparent"></div>
</div>

<div class="mt-6 border-t rule"></div>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="https://na02.patientnow.com/a/dessencewellness/OnlineBooking.aspx" class="btn btn-primary">Book consultation</a>
          <a href="tel:+17163038963" class="btn btn-outline">Call clinic</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pb-12 md:pb-16 -mt-12 md:-mt-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
        <div class="md:col-span-7">
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Why patients choose this</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-300">Vortex technology gently clears pores while infusing targeted serums for hydration and clarity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Key points</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 [counter-reset:step]">
              <li class='flex gap-3'><span class='i'>✓</span><span>Immediate luminosity</span></li>
<li class='flex gap-3'><span class='i'>✓</span><span>No downtime</span></li>
<li class='flex gap-3'><span class='i'>✓</span><span>Suitable for most skin types</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-8 bg-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Step‑by‑step process</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 [counter-reset:step]">
          <li><span class='n'></span>Skin assessment and tip selection</li>
<li><span class='n'></span>Cleansing and exfoliation</li>
<li><span class='n'></span>Painless extraction with vortex technology</li>
<li><span class='n'></span>Targeted serums and hydration</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Ideal candidates</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1"><li>Dullness, rough texture, congestion</li>
<li>Sensitive skin needing a gentle boost</li>
<li>Pre‑event refresh</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contraindications</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1"><li>Open lesions or active infection</li>
<li>Allergy to specific solutions</li>
<li>Recent aggressive peels/laser</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Risks & side effects</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1"><li>Temporary pinkness</li>
<li>Mild tightness</li>
<li>Occasional sensitivity to actives</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Aftercare</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1"><li>Gentle routine 24h</li>
<li>Avoid retinoids for 24–48h</li>
<li>SPF to maintain glow</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border p-6 bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Results & maintenance</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">Smoother texture and refined pores immediately after treatment; maintain monthly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
        <figure class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-white/10">
          <img src="/og-default.jpg" alt="Hydrafacial® / Deep Cleanse before and after (placeholder)" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-auto" />
        </figure>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Before & After</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-300">Explore real patient transformations to set realistic expectations for outcomes and timelines.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost mt-6" href="/gallery/hydrafacial">Before &amp; After Gallery</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    ol [class~="n"]::before, ol li::marker { content: none; }
    ol li { counter-increment: step; position: relative; padding-left: 2.5rem; }
    ol li .n { position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:9999px;
                background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 30% 20%, rgba(59,130,246,.9), rgba(236,72,153,.85));
                box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25); }
    ul li .i { display:inline-flex; width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
                border-radius:9999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
